{"tid":2046781,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"發現如果果區周圍都冇公屋既話真係差極有限","createTime":"2020-06-01T15:36:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T01:52:35.000Z","uid":155883,"like":14,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"eb467db273d37df60d0d4456fda5cdecdb11a33e","tid":2046781,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:36:53.000Z","msg":"我指既「一區」係指小社區, 唔係香港果啲劃分「18區」<br />\n鄰國叫「小區」我唔知香港叫咩<br />\n<br />\n例如: 鑽石山 (鳳德都隔條天橋), 鑽石山有商場有戲院, 日用品都齊哂, 交通方便入沙田又近, 遲啲沙中線直接過海<br />\n<br />\n荃灣西, 近海邊果一帶都唔錯, 海之戀商場間大快活仲要望海, 附近個康文仲要岩岩先落成, 有海濱花園跑步。荃灣既公屋大部分都係山上面<br />\n<br />\n紅磡至尖沙嘴一帶, 我指既紅磡唔係紅磡區, 而係黨鐵附近, 大家都知紅磡黨鐵站地理上並不屬於紅磡<br />\n<br />\n仲有黃埔, 呢一區除左老闆芬之外都冇咩缺點, 附近真係零公屋"},{"pid":"98952fd900bbd95d088e29ab878f532ef92d8561","tid":2046781,"uid":228143,"like":7,"dislike":17,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:40:25.000Z","msg":"私樓先最多深藍  <br />\n睇立會票站<br />\n私樓區藍比例好重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7102bcd026e2d4c64c8b41f5af9b9f004f55923","tid":2046781,"uid":11388,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T23:05:49.000Z","msg":"黃埔附近有紅磡邨"},{"pid":"03aad998cbcb8982a24bc34fc694cfdd8983f1ff","tid":2046781,"uid":115,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T01:07:25.000Z","msg":"咁講太古贏撚哂"},{"pid":"d2049d4d28bcba184d397b360894ba8abad04085","tid":2046781,"uid":268516,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"03aad998cbcb8982a24bc34fc694cfdd8983f1ff","tid":2046781,"uid":115,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T01:07:25.000Z","msg":"咁講太古贏撚哂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T01:11:51.000Z","msg":"然後無咗隻耳仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea651600da3e249efc1c60fe8fd56a80bbc49670","tid":2046781,"uid":27605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T01:13:45.000Z","msg":"屯門"},{"pid":"c7e4c73612c90427b6d7958fa0682ff489f46ea0","tid":2046781,"uid":170979,"like":3,"